James Arnold Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Arnold_Taylor 0 James Arnold Taylor (born July 22, 1969) is an American voice actor, known for portraying Ratchet in the Ratchet Clank franchise; the main character Tidus in Final Fantasy X; and Obi-Wan Kenobi in the Star Wars animated features such as Star Wars: The Clone Wars and the franchise's video games.
